The Best Giraffe Costume For Toddlers on Sale

Where can you find the best giraffe costume for toddlers?

Let's face it, the giraffe is one of a kind and makes a unique costume idea for parties, dress up and Halloween. This page showcases a wonderful selection of cute and cuddly giraffe costumes for babies and toddlers, kids and adults. We have included all you will need to create your own giraffe costume from videos and links for costumes and makeup and for giraffe costume accessories.

 
Have fun playing the part of this gentle giant. Scroll through for ideas for the perfect animal costume.

Best Giraffe Costumes on Sale

Velvety soft, this plush giraffe costume is just the thing for dressing your toddler in on Halloween night. It features a one-piece jumpsuit with horns tail and feet covers.

What a great little costume for your little one's first Halloween. The jumpsuit is warm and comfortable and the giraffe print and gentle giraffe face will make her look adorable. There are mitts to keep her warm and shoe covers to complete the outfit. Easy snaps closures for those essential nappy changes.
